  "projectDescription": "Riftmap scans your GitHub or GitLab organization, automatically discovers cross-repo dependencies across every ecosystem, and gives you a queryable dependency graph with impact analysis — so you can answer 'If I change repo X, what else breaks?' before you merge.",
